            <thetext>The scrollbars of the &quot;qui.ui.form.TextArea&quot; widget are display even if they are not needed - seen in IE8. 

FF3.6 does not show the scrollbars.

Use this code in the playground application (http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/playground) to reproduce the bug:

var textarea = new qx.ui.form.TextArea().set({
  width : 200,
  height: 100
});

var doc = this.getRoot();
doc.add(textarea,
{
  left : 100,
  top  : 50
});</thetext>
